Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
timing_constr...limit_override(25.10)    timing_constr...limit_override(25.10)

Name
       timing_constraint_enable_drv_limit_override

Syntax
       timing_constraint_enable_drv_limit_override {true | false}

       Default: true

       Controls support of the DRV override flow.

       When  set  to true, the software allows you to override the limits from
       other sources, such as, library or constraints. To  use  this  feature,
       you can specify the -override parameter with the following commands:

              * set_max_capacitance

              * set_max_transition

              * set_max_fanout

              * set_min_capacitance

              * set_min_transition

              * set_min_fanout

       When specified, the software forces a specific constraint value for the
       specified  list  of instance pins, ports, or library cell pins to over-
       ride the maximum/minimum values set prior to these constraint settings.

       To set this global variable, use the set command.

